data.description: *Sellers will contribute $5,000 towards buying closing costs or buy down points* **BEAUTIFUL POOL HOME** This stunning home is located in Palencia North Subdivision with endless activities to do for the whole family. As you drive up to the home, enjoy the beautiful landscaping and the Etched Glass Front Door. When you enter the home you will notice a seperated formal living and dining room that could be converted into a kid room / office flex space. The main living area has a fireplace with builtin shelves surrounding it. The master bedroom has plantation shutters on the windows, separated double vanity sinks in the master bathroom with a garden soaking tub and a walk in shower. The HEATED salt water pool was installed in 2019 with a separate heater from the spa. The Spa is connected to the pool to help heat the pool as well during the cooler months in FL. Some other features and improvements to the home include a complete HVAC system installed in 2023, the irrigation system has been recently inspected / tested, the Pool has been recently inspected by Red Rhino with a New Pool Filter and New reverse installed as well.  Palencia North offers endless fun for the whole family. Within the community you will find a Golf Course, Multiple Resort Pools with water slides and a splash pad. Love to work out and be fit then the stunning Clubhouse offers a full gym with all the equipment. Some other family fun activities are tennis and basketball courts, multiple playgrounds, a fenced in dog park, and a Boardwalk through Marshall Creek. The question you need to ask yourself is why you haven't scheduled your tour today.
